    {"num":"03","slug":"mono-pong","author":"jchris","live":true,"title":"PONG RUMBLE","tagline":"Mouse vs AI. First to eleven.","desc":"Two-player pong, mouse controls left paddle, AI on right. First to eleven. Ball speeds up each volley. Monochrome pixel look."},
